message:
Sukiyaki Beef is good. 

Spicy garlic pork cutlet is good. 

Prom belly katsu don is good! 

Thunder fries with mentai sauce sibei good!
One of my fav store for pork collar. However, today there are a few pieces of burnt meat 😓
Delicious food, prompt delivery and excellent service!! 💯💯💯

Super valued for money. Super affordable but yet restaurant standard sukiyaki beef don😍 

Have been returning weekly to satisfy my cravings😁

Yes, friendly staffs too🤣

Definitely a surprise find at punggol. Really affordable Japanese food at a kpt.
People behind the counter were really nice and friendly.
Ordered a pork belly katsu Don, a katsu platter and an extra serving of rice with onsen egg. And its all less than $20. 😜😜
Food is on point. Portions were big.
Surely coming back for more.

This place is certainly not 5stars worthy 

Tried the Pork Katsu don & Beef don 

Both fell way below expectations 

Katsu was soggy & Beef was tough

Had it at Marine Parade outlet

Punggol outlet might be better
Our 1st groupbuy with them . Communication is good and it arrived hot hot :) . Portion is quite generous as well . Do give them a try .

十分推荐这家👍👍👍食物好吃又便宜，比起餐厅水准更高，食材都很新鲜。
很多人点餐，但是他们效率很高很快，美味佳肴都是值得等待的😄😄
Potato salad是我的最爱，但是数量有限，要早去买，哈哈
Power !!!👍👍

Good Jap food at affordable pricing.
Not to mention that their improved significantly on the waiting time.
Best best best jap hawker style food I ever had! 👍👍👍👍
Pork Belly Katsu Don is very delicious and ingredients use were fresh. Recommended to my colleagues for their next lunch choice :)
Yummzzz! Unexpectedly good Don.... and love the chicken Karaage w/curry sauce!
food is fantastic.. fresh ingredient. yummy😋😋.. must try.!
Fresh ingredients, authentic and special cuisines with a delicate personal touch.😋😋😋
